# Render portal — commit changes

When you edit anything that affects the site hosted on Render (files under `public/`, or `server.js` routes used by the admin UI or mobile clients), finish the task with a **git commit** in this `pm-app-backend` repository using a clear, conventional message. Do not leave portal or API changes uncommitted unless the user explicitly asked not to commit.
